<topic id="supported-schema-types">
  <title>Supported Schema Types for XML Documents</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>XML documents<indexterm>Supported schema types</indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>Supported schema types for XML documents</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p><?oxy_comment_start author="Steven" timestamp="20160803T161530+0300" comment="Merge this info to parent topic and move this to not_used"?>The
      following schema types are supported:<?oxy_comment_end?></p>
    <ul>
      <li>W3C XML Schema 1.0 and 1.1 (with and without embedded Schematron rules)</li>
      <li>DTD</li>
      <li>Relax NG - XML syntax (with and without embedded Schematron rules)</li>
      <li>Relax NG - compact syntax</li>
      <li>NVDL</li>
      <li>Schematron (both ISO Schematron and Schematron 1.5)</li>
    </ul>
  </body>
